00:05:16.760 --> 00:05:18.280
You have my red thread coins.

00:05:18.760 --> 00:05:21.440
That way, I won't forget you

00:05:21.920 --> 00:05:24.200
and you won't forget me.

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:32.600
But this is what your mother left you.

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:33.720
Without it,

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:35.560
without it.

