00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:04.600
After I was arrested by human traffickers,

00:06:05.200 --> 00:06:06.520
after I was caught by a trafficker.

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.480
The Communist Party saved me.

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:12.600
Then I went to Yan'an.

00:06:12.920 --> 00:06:14.800
I've been studying and living in Yan'an.

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:17.320
Then I joined the revolution.

00:06:17.960 --> 00:06:20.360
He was sent to Shanzhou recently.

00:06:20.720 --> 00:06:22.400
